data.description: Welcome to the epitome of Texas living in this stunning custom 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, 2-story home in Longview, TX. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light that fills the space. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. A pantry and mud room with a utility room provide practicality and convenience. All three spacious bedrooms are located upstairs for privacy, and the primary bedroom boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a glass stand-up shower and a separate tub, both surrounded by custom tile work. With two living areas, a cozy fireplace and a formal dining space, you'll have plenty of room for entertaining and relaxation. Step outside, and you'll discover a true outdoor paradise, including an above-ground pool for hot summer days, a dedicated kids' play area, a covered back patio for al fresco dining, and even a workshop/storage area for your creative endeavors. All of this sits on a generous 0.39-acre corner lot, making this property the perfect blend of modern comfort and outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to call this dream home yours - schedule a viewing today!
